o<on_abort> sub

; No motion here — e-stop / abort leaves the machine disabled, so G0/G1
; would error: "need to be enabled, in coord mode for linear move".
; XY/Z park is only from the Manual Tool Change ABORT button
; (o<abort_tool_change>) after a normal program.abort while still enabled.

M5 (Spindle Stop)
M9 (Coolant Off)
M63 P0 (Restore contact probe mux — laser M62 must not block homing/jog)
M50 P1
G90 (Absolute Positioning)
G40 (Cancel Cutter Radius Compensation)
G49

o<on_abort> endsub
M2 (end program)
